quran[9{c,v,t}:
3,62,"yeh bilkul sahih waqeat hain, aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ke siwa koi khudawand nahi hai, aur woh Allah hi ki hasti hai jis ki taaqat sab se baala aur jis ki hikmat nizaam aalam mein car farma hai"
3,63,pas agar yeh log ( iss shart par muqaabla mein anay se ) mun morhin to ( unn ka mufsid hona saaf khil jaye ga ) aur Allah to mfsdon ke haal se waaqif hi hai
3,64,"kaho,"" ae ahal kitaab! aao aik aisi baat ki taraf jo hamaray aur tumahray darmain yaksaa hai yeh ke hum Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karen, is ke sath kisi ko shareek nah tehra-ayn aur hum mein se koi Allah ke siwa kisi ko apna Rab nah bana le"" is dawat ko qubool karne se agar woh mun morhin to saaf keh do ke gawah raho, hum to muslim ( sirf khuda ki bandagi o itaat karne walay ) hain"
3,65,ae ahal kitaab! tum ibrahim ke baray mein hum se kyun jhagra karte ho? torat aur injeel to ibrahim ke baad hi nazil hui hain phir kya tum itni baat bhi nahi samajte
3,66,"tum log jin cheezon ka ilm rakhtay ho unn mein to khoob bhsin kar chuke, ab un mamlaat mein kyun behas karne chalay ho jin ka tumahray paas kuch bhi ilm nahi Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
3,67,"ibrahim nah yahodi tha nah isaai, balkay woh aik muslim yaksu tha aur woh hargiz mushrikon mein se nah tha"
3,68,ibrahim se nisbat rakhnay ka sab se ziyada haq agar kisi ko pohanchana hai to unn logon ko pohanchana hai jinhon ne is ki pairwi ki aur ab yeh nabi aur is ke maan-ne walay iss nisbat ke ziyada haq daar hain Allah sirf aُnhi ka haami o madadgaar hai jo imaan rakhtay hon
3,69,"( ae imaan laane walo ) ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh chahta hai ke kisi terhan tumhe raah raast se hata day, halaank Dur haqeeqat woh apne siwa kisi kogumrahi mein nahi daal rahay hain magar inhen is ka shaoor nahi hai"
3,70,ae ahal kitaab! kyun Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar karte ho halaank tum khud un ka mushahida kar rahay ho ?
